dct_description_sm: Published in: A new, authentic and complete collection of voyages around the world, undertaken and performed by royal authority ... / by G. W. Anderson. Bound between p. 284 and 285. Relief shown by hachures. Includes inset of Gowers I., Carterets Island and Simsons I. Includes Trevanions Island, Lord Egmont's Island or New Guernsey, Lord Howe's Island or New Jersey, Lord Edgcombe's Island or New Sark, Ourry's Island or New Alderney, Swallow's Island. The site of a volcano is marked.
